Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:28.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我的心中充满永远的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:36.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢上某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甚至会改变未来
